text: Aerest of blacan broce on taan.
Þonne ofdune on taan of beaddig broc þonne upp on beadding broc on halgan welle.
Þanon of halgan wylle on curig ie mære upp on æt guldæs geate þonne to readan flodan.
Þonne upp on igen stream to orcerdcumbe.
Fram mædwegum to fearnleage on þa stigele.
An gemærhagan to hrimwoldes beorge to þæm ealdan wege.
Of wice rycge ofdune on þone eastenan stream andlang streames to buchanforda.
Ðonon west be wyrrttrume to egwulfes gemære.
Ðonne to wealacan dic to ludanalrum.
Þonne andlang streames to wisforda ufanwerdu.
Þonne suð on þa foryrþe to þæm beorge ofdune to þæm wylle.
Ðonne forðrihte to broce ofer wiðan mæd.
